title: Print an Intent to Release form
custom_preconds:
GIVEN the user has opened a Release tx
AND the Intent to Release checkbox is checked
AND the user has permissions
custom_steps: WHEN the user clicks Print>Intent to Release Form
custom_expected: THEN the form will print in PDF and follow the proper format

title: Create New Rule 6 Return Process tx
custom_preconds: GIVEN the user has clicked Create New>Major Transactions>Assignments>Rule 6 Return Process
custom_expected:
THEN IF no preliminary, submitted or rejected transaction created within 10 days of the current date exists, the system will load a new Preliminary transaction
AND The Text on the form is dynamic and should be updated when the user adjusts the tender date and time displayed

title: Prevented from creating tx for a player not belonging to my Club
custom_preconds: GIVEN user is logged in as club
custom_steps: WHEN the user opens the tx for a player from a different ORG
custom_expected: THEN system displays error message: "You do not have permission to create a transaction for a player that belongs to another Organization."

title: Prevented from creating tx for player who has already been returned
custom_preconds: GIVEN user has created the tx for a player already returned to the ORG they were drafted by in most recent R5 draft
custom_expected: THEN system displays error message: "Player has already been returned."

title: Submit a Rule 6 Return to another Club
custom_preconds: GIVEN the user has opened a Preliminary or Rejected tx
custom_expected:
THEN System will run rule checks
AND Update Status to Pending to Club
AND tx reloads in view mode
AND Successful notification displays (tx does NOT appear in Player History)

title: View existing Rule 6 Return
custom_preconds: GIVEN user has searched for an existing tx
custom_steps: WHEN the user clicks on the tx
custom_expected:
THEN tx displays in view or edit mode
AND Close button works

title: Receive error if creating tx for player who is not at the MJ Level
custom_preconds: GIVEN user has created the tx for a Minor League Player
custom_expected: THEN system shows error message: This transaction is for Major League players only

title: BOC permissions
custom_expected:
The transaction has a view permission set that can be added to an existing user if needed. Users without the permission cannot view the form anywhere in the system.

ADMINS:
Can view and Print all major league transactions [Club and BOC] in all states for Major League Players.
Can view all flags for all transactions and transaction attachments in all states.
Can create, delete, edit, e-sign and submit all Major league transactions for Major League players. 
Can Approve, Reject, Reverse and Suppress all Major League transactions and see associated Flags.

BASIC:
Can view and Print all major league transactions [Club and BOC] in all states for Major League Players but cannot make any changes or e-sign.
Can view all flags for all transactions and transaction attachments in all states.

title: Club user rejects Rule 6 Return tx
custom_preconds: GIVEN user has a submitted tx
custom_expected:
THEN successful notification displays
AND item is removed from clipboard

title: Receive error creating a tx for player that has a pending or approved tx after entered Assignment date
custom_preconds: GIVEN the player has a pending or approved tx after assignment date tx
custom_expected: THEN show error: A transaction cannot occur before the date of the player's latest approved or pending transaction, on <TX Date>.

title: Receive error if assignment date is back or future more than 10 days
custom_preconds: GIVEN the user has back/future dated the tx more than 10 days
custom_expected: THEN show error: Assignment Date must be within 10 days of submission.

title: Receive error attempting to do a tx for a player with a submitted waiver request
custom_preconds: GIVEN the player has submitted waiver request
custom_expected: THEN show error: Player with a submitted waiver request may not be assigned.  The waiver request should be deleted before re-submitting the assignment.

title: Receive error Accepting/Rejected a tx for player who has a pending or approved tx after current date
custom_preconds: GIVEN player has a pending/approved tx after the tx date
custom_steps: WHEN user clicks accept/reject on the tx
custom_expected:
THEN show error: A transaction cannot occur before the date of the player's latest approved or pending transaction, on <TX Date>.
AND clicking back will return user to point of entry

title: Receive error if the player has an unexpired waiver request bulletin
custom_preconds: GIVEN player has an unexpired waiver request
custom_steps: WHEN the user clicks submit on the tx
custom_expected: THEN show error: Player is currently on a pending waiver request bulletin and may not be outrighted to the minor leagues.

title: Delete a Rule 6 Return tx
custom_preconds: GIVEN user has a preliminary or rejected tx
custom_expected:
THEN show message: Are you sure you want to delete this [form]? ("Form" to be replaced with transaction type)
IF yes THEN record deleted AND successful notification displays AND user returned to point of entry
IF no THEN user returns to form AND no action taken

title: Receive Notification when Rule 6 Return is accepted or rejected
custom_preconds: GIVEN user has a submitted tx
custom_steps: WHEN the tx is accepted or rejected
custom_expected:
THEN notification displays in initiating clubs clipboard
AND links work

title: Prevented from initiating a tx for a player that was not selected in the most recent Rule 5 Draft
custom_preconds: GIVEN user is creating the tx for a player not in the most recent R5 Draft
custom_expected: THEN user gets error: Player was not selected in the Rule 5 Draft.

title: Club user receives an Action item when a rule 6 return process is submitted
custom_preconds: GIVEN user has a submitted tx
custom_steps: WHEN the user views their action items
custom_expected:
THEN tx displays in clipboard
AND links work

title: Receive error if the player does not have a valid roster status
custom_preconds: GIVEN the player does NOT have status of Active Pending Contract, Designated for Assignment, Not to Report, Not Yet Reported or Active
custom_expected: THEN show error: Player must be Active, Not to Report, Not yet reported, Active Pending Contract or Designated for Assignment to be assigned.

title: Edit existing Rule 6 Return tx
custom_preconds:
GIVEN user has permissions
AND tx is in preliminary or rejected state
custom_expected:
THEN save button will appear
AND form will reload in edit mode

title: Receive error if player does not have Outright Waivers secured
custom_preconds: GIVEN a player does not have Outright waivers secured
custom_steps: WHEN the user clicks submit on the tx
custom_expected: THEN user gets error: Outright assignment waivers must be in effect for this assignment.

custom_steps:
WHEN user advance searches for tx
AND adds filter Transaction Status= Rejected
custom_expected: THEN user can select and view tx

title: Approving Rule 5 Select tx to create a Daily Tx Bulletin
custom_preconds: GIVEN a tx is submitted
custom_expected: THEN create a transaction for it on the Daily Transaction bulletin

title: View existing Accepted Return of Rule 5 Selection tx
custom_preconds: GIVEN user wants to view an existing Return of Rule 5 Selection tx
custom_steps:
WHEN user advance searches for tx
AND adds filter Transaction Status= Accepted
custom_expected: THEN user can select and view tx

custom_expected:
THEN they are able to attach files

Club permissions

title: Receive error when creating an Option if the player requires Optional Waivers
custom_preconds: GIVEN a player does not have a secured Optional Waiver
custom_steps:
WHEN user tries to create an Optional Assignment for that player
AND has an outright trade effective the day of the option or the day prior and was on option prior to trade or was designated from option prior to trade
custom_expected: THEN user should be able to create an Optional Assignment for player with no error

title: Approving Selection to ML roster tx to update player's info
custom_preconds: GIVEN user creates a Selection to ML roster tx for a player
custom_expected:
THEN * Set the player’s club to the target/destination club
* Set the player’s level of play to the level of the target/destination club
* If player’s rookie flag is not set and the rookie milestone date is not set, then set the player’s rookie flag.
* Set the player’s highest level of play.
* If the player's first MJ Lg acquisition org is blank, then set the player’s first MJ Lg acquisition org to their current org.
* If the player's first MJ Lg acquisition date is blank, then set the player's first MJ Lg acquisition date to the transaction's date. 
* If the player's first MJ Lg acquisition from club is blank, then set the player's first MJ Lg acquisition from club to their previous club.
* If it's during the season and the First MJ Lg report date org is null, set the player’s first MJ Lg report date org.
* If it's during the season and The First MJ Lg report date is null, set the player’s first MJ Lg report date to the report date from the transaction.
* If it’s during the season and the current MJ Lg club report date is null, set the player’s current MJ Lg club report date.
* Set the player’s current major league acquisition org to their current Org. 
* Set the player’s current MJ Lg acquisition date to the transaction date
* Set the current club acquired from to the assignor club
